# MDR-S1 hygiene (2026-04-18) — local auditing artifacts that must not
# ship in the repo. If a committed copy exists it should be removed via
# `git rm -r --cached <path>` before these entries take effect.
screenshots/career_deeplink_*/
screenshots/career_persona_*/
